==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: invisible ink
<hw>in*vis"i*ble ink`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A fluid that has no color
in the visible spectrum, but may be detected under certain conditions,
as under ultraviolet light. It may be used to write notes not readable
under normal light.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Invisibleness</ent>⟦br⟧
